# Phase 1: Analyze the Fix

This is a patch for SLPVectorizer:

[SLP]Initial compatibility support for shl v, 1 and add v, v
Allows to make shl v, 1 to be compatible with add operations by
modeling it as add v,v

Fixes #40801

